
Preparation after checkout
--------------------------

  After checking out this package, you can build it with

    autoreconf --install
    ./configure
    make
    make package


Preparation before release
---------------------------

  * read CHANGES
  * run 'make distcheck'
      - there should be no errors
  * run 'make dist' 
      - check that all gssapi/windows files are actually there
  * run 'make package'
      - inspect entire contents of the created 'destdir' directory


